{
  "id": "adv_event_2406_02_04",
  "title": "リズノワ_お褒めの言葉はこころまで.mov",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rio-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、もう撮ってるの？\n……葵？　もうっ何か言いなさいよ……始めるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ are you filming already?\n…Aoi? Geez‚ say something… Let’s start.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 9.1570979118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rio-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、いつもありがとう\n今のリズノワがあるのは貴方のおかげよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ thank you for everything.\nThe current LizNoir exists because of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.3666669209,
      "endTime": 15.6583451589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rio-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "一人一人の活動の幅を広げてくれたし\nアイドル活動にも集中させてもらえてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve broadened the scope of our individual activities‚\nand we’ve been able to focus on our idol activities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.8666669209,
      "endTime": 21.6388210614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rio-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "これからも辛いことや嬉しいこと、沢山あると思うけど\n一緒に前に進んでいきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think there will be a lot of hardships and joys in the future‚\nbut let’s move forward together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8333335876,
      "endTime": 28.485510253799998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rio-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "……えっ？　「そんな定型文みたいでいいのか？」\n私はちゃんと自分の感謝の気持ちを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? “Is it okay to sound so stereotypical?”\nI’m properly conveying my feelings of gratitude…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.7000001271,
      "endTime": 35.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rio-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "「全部吐き出しちゃいなよ」って……\n葵！　変なこと言わないでよ！　まったく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Just let it all out.”\nAoi! Don’t say weird things! Geez…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1333334605,
      "endTime": 42.1607256573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rio-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "これ以上何を話せって言うのよ。葵がからかうから\n変な空気になっちゃったじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What else am I supposed to say? Thanks to Aoi teasing me‚\nthe atmosphere’s gotten weird.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3666665395,
      "endTime": 48.310022385900005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rio-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……あっ、そういえばね、また偶然予定が合えば\n実家にご飯でも食べに来てくれないかしら……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… Ah‚ by the way‚ if our schedules happen to match up again by chance‚\nwould you like to come over to my parents’ house for dinner…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4999998729,
      "endTime": 56.8080040614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rio-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "その……お母さんも貴方に会いたがってたから\n貴方さえ良ければだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… My mom also wanted to meet you.\nIf you’re okay with it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9999998729,
      "endTime": 63.593741576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rio-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "も、もちろん偶然よ、偶然予定が合えばの話よ！？\nそもそも岡山って遠いんだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-of course it’d have to be by chance‚ if our schedules happen to match up!\nOkayama’s far away anyway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7999998729,
      "endTime": 70.8312470119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rio-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "ほら！　やっぱりまた変な空気になったわ！\n葵、後でお仕置きよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look! The atmosphere’s gotten weird again!\nAoi‚ you’re getting punished later!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.4999973298,
      "endTime": 77.83040571219999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6837.706883400003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 79.1405759173
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_aoi-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "やぁやぁ、僕だよ\nいつもお世話になってるね、ありがとうありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey hey‚ it’s me.\nThanks for everything‚ I really appreciate it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.1377042132,
      "endTime": 85.47520983979999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 85.6710375465
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_aoi-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことより、莉央の動画、観てくれた？\n面白いから、ぜひ観てよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More importantly‚ did you see Rio’s video?\nIt’s interesting‚ so you should definitely watch it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.6710375465,
      "endTime": 90.43103758459999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_aoi-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、また\n……って言いたいところだけど、短過ぎるかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ see ya.\n…I want to say that‚ but is it too short?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.6377042132,
      "endTime": 97.7620807963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 93.577649752
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.1377035774
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_aoi-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "あまりに莉央がうるさいから、一人で撮ることに\nしたんだけど、それでもいろいろ言われてさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio was being so noisy that I decided to film it alone‚\nbut even then‚ I got told off about a lot of things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.1377035774,
      "endTime": 104.6177034057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_aoi-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "「真面目に、心を込めて、きっちりと言葉にして\n{user}さんに伝えなさいよ」だってさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Be serious‚ put your heart into it‚ and properly convey it\nto {user}-san with your words‚” she said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.0377019244,
      "endTime": 112.59239590940001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 112.9377037046
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_aoi-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "僕らと{user}君の間に、今更言葉なんて\nいらないと思うんだけど……しょうがないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t think words are necessary between us and you anymore…\nBut… what can you do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.9377037046,
      "endTime": 121.60221633889999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 121.7043688453
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_aoi-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "最近は、演技の仕事を沢山させてもらったね\n自分の価値観とか心情とか、いろいろ考えさせられたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lately‚ I’ve been doing a lot of acting jobs.\nIt’s made me think about a lot of things‚ like my values and feelings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.7043688453,
      "endTime": 133.26167017589998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 133.6377034502
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_aoi-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "後、こころに聞かれたんだけど、一緒に結婚式のシーン\nを練習した時、別にドキドキとかしなかったよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ and Kokoro asked me something. When we practiced the wedding scene together‚\nyou weren’t nervous or anything‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.6377034502,
      "endTime": 144.8745063143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 145.0710367835
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_aoi-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、いや、練習とはいえ、そういうのはお互い\n意識してドキドキするものだ、って言うからさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ no‚ I mean‚ even if it was practice‚\nit’s something we should both be conscious of and feel nervous about‚ she said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.0710367835,
      "endTime": 153.1583159125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_aoi-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "ドラマの再放送を観て、気になったらしいんだけど……\n今更、妙なことを聞くよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess she got curious after watching a rerun of the drama…\nTo ask something strange like that now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.3710367835,
      "endTime": 161.0710368788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 161.2710367835
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_aoi-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、こっちまで変な気分になってくるよ……\n長く喋り過ぎたね、それじゃあまた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously‚ it’s making even me feel weird…\nI talked for too long. Well then‚ see ya.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.2710367835,
      "endTime": 170.7420801794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_ai-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "はい……えっと……こ、こんにちは……！\nLizNoirの小美山愛と申す者です……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yes… Um… H-hello…!\nI’m Ai Komiyama from LizNoir…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.0420740758,
      "endTime": 181.38143889050002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_ai-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんには感謝してもしても\n足りないぐらい日々感謝していて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so grateful to {user}-san every day‚\nmore than words can say――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.5754074091,
      "endTime": 186.69295825900002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
